call.agent_name: Main Incoming Calls- Voice AI Agent
call.transcript:
Agent: Hello, this is Hannah from Fetch Recruitment. This call is recorded for quality and training purposes. How can I help you today?
User: i want to apply for a carpentry job
Agent: I can help with your job enquiry. First, what state is the job in?
User: melbourne
Agent: To get you to the right person quickly, is there a recruiter's name listed on the job ad you're calling about?
User: Lachlie
Agent: Great, I've found them. They are in our Corporate Services team. Perfect. Now I just need to get a few details to log this enquiry for the team. What’s your full name?
User: peter tron
Agent: And your best email address?
User: peter@email.com
Agent: Your phone number?
User: 0412123123
Agent: And finally, could you confirm the job title or give me a brief message to pass on?
User: ring me
Agent: Let me read that back to make sure I’ve got it right. Your name is Peter Tron, your email is peter@email.com, your phone number is 0412123123, and you're enquiring about "ring me" for our Corporate Services team—does that all sound correct, and is it okay for me to log this for the team?
User: yes
